movies.title: Victoria the Great
movies.plot: The film biography of Queen Victoria focussing initially on the early years of her reign with her marriage to Prince Albert and her subsequent rule after Albert's death in 1861.

events.title: Queen Victoria and Prince Albert marry
Edward Oxford attempts to assassinate Queen Victoria
Victoria is informed that her uncle has died, and she is now queen
Victoria is crowned Queen of England
Queen Victoria proposes to Prince Albert
